descript.abstract: State Areas (layer) is a symbolized and labeled display presentation of the Mexico States data set. The geographic and attribute data of Mexico States are symbolized and labeled to create the layer. All features are uniquely symbolized based on the COLORMAP attribute and labeled by class based on the ST_NAME attribute.
descript.purpose: State Areas (layer) provides a common and useful display of Mexico States for a better understanding of the data set contents. Add this layer to a map to display useful information about the data set and that integrates well with other data set layers.
descript.supplinf: For more information about the data set, see its metadata.
